{
  "stem": "25912.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as soon as the war ended, he was in-- at that time, he was in Italy, with the second Polish corps, which was part of the Eighth Army.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had done the Italian campaign, Monte Cassino, and all that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He and a friend took a Jeep and went to Germany to DP camps and to prisoner of war camps, armed with my photograph, trying to find out if anybody knew anything about me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In one POW camp, they found somebody who had known me in the Warsaw Rising, who said, well, she was alive at the end of August, but don't know what happened after that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then finally, he found Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Wedecka's daughter in a POW camp, where she was taken at the end of the Warsaw Rising, when the Germans recognized the Polish Home Army, gave them prisoner of war rights under the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said that she knew that I had survived and had been taken out of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I don't know at which point we heard, but it must have been about September, October, that we had news that Father was alive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we assumed that so was George.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then one day, beginning of November, '45, we were in the room we were renting, when two people turned up, a man and a woman, Jewish, with a note in my father's handwriting, saying, trust them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm waiting for you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then my mother said, you know, what is the plan?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, well, they was, they are collecting a group of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they will guide us out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father's waiting in Linz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- In Austria?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Austria.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they will get us there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no question.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just up and left.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
